         <projectDesc>
            <p xml:lang="en"><ref target="https://www.clarin.eu/parlamint">ParlaMint</ref> is a project that aims to (1) create a multilingual set of comparable corpora of parliamentary proceedings uniformly encoded according to the <ref target="https://clarin-eric.github.io/ParlaMint/">ParlaMint encoding guidelines</ref>, covering the period from 2015 to mid-2022; (2) add linguistic annotations to the corpora and machine-translate them to English; (3) make the corpora available through concordancers; and (4) build use cases in Political Sciences and Digital Humanities based on the corpus data.</p>
